DAY 3 — HOW CODE RUNS
--------------------
Execution Flow
--------------
.java → javac → .class → JVM → Output

Compiler
-------
Converts source code into bytecode

JVM (Java Virtual Machine)
--------------------------
Runs bytecode
Platform independent

JVM Components
--------------
Class Loader
Bytecode Verifier
Execution Engine
  
Memory Areas
------------  
Heap → Objects
Stack → Method calls
Metaspace → Class info

JIT Compiler
-------------
Converts bytecode to machine code for faster execution
  
Garbage Collection
------------------
Removes unused objects
